// The PIRATE CAPTAIN boss at the back of his CASTAWAY SHORE camp — the climax of
// the shore. Flagged `boss` for the boss theme. Beating him (and clearing the rest
// of the beach) fires the level's `captain_joins` clear cutscene, which recruits
// him. Not invincible — a hard but winnable fight.
EncounterDef(id: "pirate_captain", enemies: ["pirate_captain"], boss: true)
